short.ar: العب لعبة tic tac toe ضد الكمبيوتر باستخدام أحرف X و O.

short.ta: எக்ஸ் மற்றும் ஓ எழுத்துக்களைப் பயன்படுத்தி கணினிக்கு எதிராக டிக் டாக் டோ விளையாட்டை விளையாடுங்கள்.

short.tr: X ve O karakterlerini kullanarak bilgisayara karşı tic tac toe oyunu oynayın.
short.uk: Грайте в хрестики-нулики проти комп’ютера, використовуючи символи X і O.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The tic tac toe game consists of 9 squares, three rows and three columns.  Play a game of tic tac toe against the computer using X and O characters. 

 You can win points by placing the letter X horizontally, vertically or diagonally.  The scoreboard appears at the top of the screen.  You have to make moves to prevent the computer from scoring points.  Try to beat the computer in this way.  In every move you make, think about two or three moves ahead.  In this way, place the letter O in one of the boxes, calculating in your mind the combinations of all the moves that your opponent is likely to make.


To swipe Install this extension to play the Tic Tac Toe game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
